<article class="heist-overlay__section heist-prose-section"
         data-section="faqs"
         data-overlay-panel-target="section"
         hidden>
  <h2 class="heist-prose-section__title">FAQS</h2>

  <dl class="heist-prose-section__faqs">
    <div>
      <dt>Who can join?</dt>
      <dd>Anyone with an email and something to build.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Do I have to stream?</dt>
      <dd>No. The stream is run for you, not by you. Watch when you want, ship when you can.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>What counts toward the 1,000 hours?</dt>
      <dd>Every hour anyone in the program logs to Hackatime over the weekend, on any project, in any language, on any platform.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>What gets unlocked?</dt>
      <dd>Three prizes. One at 300 hours. One at 600. One at 1,000. Each is announced live on stream, in the order they're earned.</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Do I need to be online the whole weekend?</dt>
      <dd>No. Hackatime counts your hours whether you're tuned in or not.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</article>